@startuml
actor Client
participant CommentsController
participant Comment

Client -> CommentsController: DELETE request to /comments/{id} with x-auth-token header
note right of Client: Client requests comment deletion
activate CommentsController

CommentsController -> Comment: delete(id)
note right of CommentsController: Delete comment from database
activate Comment
Comment --> CommentsController: Return boolean result
deactivate Comment

CommentsController --> Client: Return boolean result as JSON response
note right of CommentsController: Send deletion result to client
deactivate CommentsController
@enduml